### ===== EXPECTED RESULTS =====

### ✅ PolicyCreated Event:
### - RabbitMQ routing key: "policy.created"
### - ChatService receives notification
### - SignalR broadcasts: "🎉 New Policy Created!"

### ✅ PolicyTerminated Event:
### - RabbitMQ routing key: "policy.terminated"
### - ChatService receives notification
### - SignalR broadcasts: "🚫 Policy Terminated"

### ✅ ProductActivated Event:
### - RabbitMQ routing key: "product.activated"
### - ChatService receives notification
### - SignalR broadcasts: "✨ Product Activated!"

### 🔍 How to verify:
### 1. Open client-app/index.html
### 2. Connect as agent
### 3. Use buttons: "Create Policy", "Terminate Policy", "Activate Product"
### 4. Watch real-time notifications appear
### 5. Check browser console for SignalR logs